title: Scandal (1989) DVD Rip
description:
Scandal

An English bon-vivant osteopath is enchanted with a young exotic 
dancer and invites her to live with him. He serves as friend and 
mentor, and through his contacts and parties she and her friend meet
and date members of the Conservative Party. Eventually a scandal
occurs when her affair with the Minister of War goes public,
threatening their lifestyles and their freedom. Based on the real
Profumo scandal of 1963.
